      "comment": "DON'T (2) lightly raced gelding resuming. Showed ability on debut last December but disappointed in his two subsequent runs. Back without a trial and bred to be a swimmer. NA HAMAH (10) consistent mare who returned with a gritty on-pace second over this track and trip. Buckley sticks from the good gate and has solid claims. RAINING LUCK (5) tough ask on resumption from the wide gate with a battling eighth over 900m at Newcastle in the heavy going. Ran fourth here last time in and gets a better setup for this. THE CRUSHER (4) Astern gelding from Gladtobehome on debut for the Allan Kehoe yard. Latest trial placing over 845m at Wyong looked sound. Expected to take a hand in the finish.",
